---
title: Mexican Black Bean Chilli with Cheesy Kumara Topping & Charred Corn
description: We've packed this bake with classic Mexican flavours, with a spicy kick for those who want it! The rich black bean chilli gets topped with tender cubes of kumara plus a scattering of cheese. Plus, try our technique for sweet and smokey charred corn - one bite and you'll be hooked!
